    .container
      .row.mb-4
        .col-sm-12.text-center
          h4.title.text-purple FAQ
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          #faqAccordian.accordian
            .card
              .card-header.px-2
                h5.mb-0
                  button(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1").btn.btn-link.faq-heading.text-dark.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center How does it work?
                    img(src="/images/shape.png")
              div(aria-labelledby="heading1" data-parent="#faqAccordian")#collapse1.collapse
                .card-body
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 Quadency is a unified digital asset management platform. By connecting your existing accounts from popular exchanges such as Binance, Bittrex, and Coinbase Pro, you can enjoy all the benefits our platform has to offer.
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 Accounts can be connected to Quadency using API keys. To learn more about how API keys work, <a href="https://support.quadency.com/setup-and-exchange-linking/what-are-exchange-apis" target="_blank">click here</a>. All information is stored securely and kept in sync as you use the platform.
            .card
              .card-header.px-2
                h5.mb-0
                  button(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3").btn.btn-link.collapsed.faq-heading.text-dark.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center Which exchanges are supported?
                    img(src="/images/shape.png")
              div(aria-labelledby="heading3" data-parent="#faqAccordian")#collapse3.collapse
                .card-body
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 As of today, we have integrations with Coinbase Pro (formerly GDAX), Binance, Bittrex, KuCoin, Poloniex, OKEx, Kraken, Bitfinex, and Gemini.
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 Several more are in progress, and new exchanges will continually be added - prioritized by trading volume, growth, liquidity, and of course user feedback. All integrations are thoroughly tested and undergo a rigorous roll-out process to ensure the safety of your funds.
            .card
              .card-header.px-2
                h5.mb-0
                  button(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4").btn.btn-link.faq-heading.text-dark.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center Is it secure?
                    img(src="/images/shape.png")
              div(aria-labelledby="heading4" data-parent="#faqAccordian")#collapse4.collapse
                .card-body
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 Yes! Quadency employs numerous security measures to keep your accounts secure from unauthorized access, including encryption of API keys, passwords, and other sensitive information, SSL over TLS for end-to-end encryption of communication, 2FA for additional security of user accounts, and we follow OWASP top 10 standards and undergo regular penetration testing by third-party security providers. <a href="https://support.quadency.com/account-and-security/is-quadency-secure" target="_blank">You can learn more about our security practices here</a>.
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 Additionally, we encourage users to disable withdrawal permissions from exchange APIs and hold non-traded funds off exchanges and in secure, hardware wallets.
            .card
              .card-header.px-2
                h5.mb-0
                  button(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5").btn.btn-link.faq-heading.text-dark.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center How much does it cost?
                    img(src="/images/shape.png")
              div(aria-labelledby="heading5" data-parent="#faqAccordian")#collapse5.collapse
                .card-body
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 Creating an account with Quadency is <strong>free!</strong> Plus, youâ€™ll get 14 days to experience Quadency Pro - which includes all the features mentioned above  - at no cost. When the trial period ends, you can continue using Quadencyâ€™s free features like portfolio monitoring across your accounts, or upgrade to Pro to keep unlimited trading, access to real-time PnL insights, and more.
            .card
              .card-header.px-2
                h5.mb-0
                  button(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6").btn.btn-link.faq-heading.text-dark.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.text-wrap.text-left Are there any per-transaction fees?
                    img(src="/images/shape.png")
              div(aria-labelledby="heading6" data-parent="#faqAccordian")#collapse6.collapse
                .card-body
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 No. Quadency does not charge any transaction fees. Any fees charged by the exchanges where you trade are paid to them directly.
            .card
              .card-header.px-2
                h5.mb-0
                  button(type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse7").btn.btn-link.faq-heading.text-dark.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.text-wrap.text-left Do you have a referral program?
                    img(src="/images/shape.png")
              div(aria-labelledby="heading7" data-parent="#faqAccordian")#collapse7.collapse
                .card-body
                  p.faq-text.text-dark.px-3.py-3 Yes, you can earn rewards by referring traders to Quadency. See our <a href="/referrals">Referral Program</a> for more details and to get started.
